HEADWORD: Herbaceous
<hw>Her*ba"ceous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>herbaceus</ets> grassy. See <er>Herb</er>.]</ety> <def>Of or
pertaining to herbs; having the nature, texture, or characteristics, of
an herb; <as>as, <ex>herbaceous</ex> plants; an <ex>herbaceous</ex>
stem.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

